name: Iso8859.Part1
comment:
Encode and decode strings according to the [ISO/IEC 8859-1](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1) encoding.

@docs decode, encode

values.name: decode
values.comment: Decode a string according to the [ISO/IEC 8859-1](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1) encoding. Returns `Nothing` if any of the characters are unsupported.

values.name: encode
values.comment: Encode a string according to the [ISO/IEC 8859-1](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1) encoding. Returns `Nothing` if any of the characters are unsupported.
